# Pest Testing

## When to use

- Writing unit or feature tests with Pest PHP
- Running Pest tests with filters, groups, or parallel execution
- Testing Laravel controllers, models, jobs, or middleware with Pest
- Testing Livewire or Filament components with Pest
- Generating code coverage reports with Pest

## Keywords

`pest`, `pest test`, `pest php`, `test coverage`, `pest parallel`, `pest filter`, `laravel testing`, `filament testing`
